{
  "stem": "19055.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So we always had the American connection, so to speak,",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I really didn't know much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All I, all I knew, this was a, a west and free life compared to communism, obviously.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I, I saw nothing negative about this country.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came in Westchester County to White Plains, White Plains Hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was an intern there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, having had five years of surgical experience in Israel, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I took a position in, in Buffalo, New York, in a medical school, and take a residency in urology.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted to get a new specialty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I became a urologist in, in Buffalo, New York, where we lived until my retirement in 1972.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in 1972, we moved to, to Florida, to Sarasota, where I have a place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the summers, we spent still in Westchester County, which was my first love in the USA.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1995, on the 50th anniversary of, of my liberation, I wrote a letter to the editor in the paper in Sarasota, which is owned by And in, in a brief letter, I, I described my liberation and who the people were who liberated me and to give a public thanks to the US Army.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can't believe the response.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I got letters, telephone calls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and I still keep contact.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the people, I took them out for dinner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were all together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a colonel who was in the 30th Infantry Unit there who is 75 years old now who became my friend.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he's my bicycle partner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And New York.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's a cliche to say this is the greatest country in the world.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
